  "text": "Gabor Filter: Mostly used contextual filter [CITATION_1] for fingerprint image enhancement is Gabor filter proposed by Hong, Wan, and Jain [CITATION_2] . Gabor filters have both frequencyselective and orientation-selective properties and they also have optimal joint resolution in both spatial and frequency domains. ",
